# PC-1: Analyze Complexity
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Algorithm or data structure selection

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Complexity Analysis: Measurement of algorithmic efficiency (time/space) using Big O notation.
- Performance Budget: Acceptable limits for response times, memory, or throughput.

ENFORCE: Estimate Big O time and space complexity for every algorithm and data structure choice.
PROHIBIT: Choosing algorithms or structures that violate defined performance budgets.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate to Performance Engineering Skill; suggest alternative algorithms.
